channel.title: Problem with windows 7
channel.description: okay im an old server owner but had to shut down my old server and it got deleted on my windows XP computer but now i have a newer faster laptop running windows 7 and it dosent work the same before i just got no-ip and utorrent then ran them went into control panel and allowed my server IP but now i dont know how to allow the server through my firewall so people can connect can anyone help with this problem? its more complicated then windows xp and it sucks :( but i like windows 7 :)
